Cell["\<\
Young's seminormal representation is not orthogonal with respect to the \
canonical Hermitian product. However, it is orthogonal with respect to a \
scalar product associated with a diagonal matrix, given by the norm squares \
of Young's seminormal basis vectors. It is demonstrated here.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->796632200,ExpressionUUID->"4264139a-b3c4-4c57-acbc-3f2b735598cf"],

